The best way to illustrate this point is with the Pareto Frontier. Modular =
extrinsic security provides benefits on two dimensions: choice and time.=C2=
=A0
In the present, allowing applications to set their own DVNs lets them choos=
e the right point on the cost-security frontier for their specific need ins=
tead of locking them into one likely suboptimal point.=C2=A0
