e: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">At its wildest, it means t=
hat developers can choose to build products that use different chains for d=
ifferent features, and that users never have to think about which chain the=
y&#8217;re on.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px=
; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Bryan Pellegrino, Ryan Zarick, an=
