ecoration: underline;">A Protocol for Packet Network Interconnection</a><sp=
an>,&#8221; in which they first described TCP and its potential to upgrade =
ARPANet, the predecessor to the internet. When the piece was published, the=
re were 558 million internet users in the world, exactly 10% of the 5.5 bil=
lion people who use the internet today.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: =
rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">M=
