eight: 1.16em; margin: 1em 0 0.625em 0; position: relative;"><strong>How In=
teroperability Protocols Compete&#160;</strong></h3><p style=3D"color: rgb(=
64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">To ge=
t widespread adoption and become the TCP/IP for blockchains, LayerZero has =
to do two things, each of which reinforces the other:</p><ol style=3D"margi=
