sizing: border-box; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 2=
6px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;"><strong>Hook into Mor=
e Chains.</strong><span> Deploy endpoints on more chains so that the protoc=
ol can serve developers and users wherever they want to operate.&#160;</spa=
n></p></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: bord=
er-box; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin:=
 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;"><strong>Integrate with More Apps =
and Protocols. </strong><span>Convince more applications and protocols to b=
uild on LayerZero to build omnichain apps or bridge their tokens by adoptin=
g the OFT Standard.&#160;</span></p></li></ol><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64=
, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">The more ch=
ains LayerZero is on, the more compelling the value prop for more apps and =
protocols.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; li=
ne-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Currently, LayerZero is live on 45+ c=
hains including Ethereum, Optimism, Arbitrum, zkSync, BNB Chain (the succes=
sor to BSC), Aptos, Celo, Scroll, Polygon, Avalanche, Fantom, and Base, wit=
h more coming soon.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size:=
 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>The most eagerly antic=
ipated is the darling of this cycle so far: </span><a href=3D"https://subst=
ack.com/redirect/e1c81732-641e-4c85-817d-b917aa1dee5a?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3Qif=
Q.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(64, =
64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">Solana</a><span>. &#8220;Solana is ba=
