entation</strong><span> of the standard in order to make it usable, the Lay=
erZero protocol is the standard and defaults are implementation. Defaults d=
on&#8217;t impact the protocol itself in any way, shape, or form, they just=
 make it easier to implement.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64=
, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">And if you =
want to build the TCP/IP for blockchains, you need developers to implement =
